OL,3,CPetition calling for climate protestor
OL,4,Cto remain in the UK reaches 169,000
OL,6,FMore than 169,000 people have now
OL,7,Fsigned a petition to prevent the
OL,8,Fdeportation of a climate activist who
OL,9,Fscaled the QEII bridge.
OL,11,FMarcus Decker, a German national, was
OL,12,Fjailed for two years and seven months
OL,13,Ffor causing a public nuisance, after
OL,14,Fthe bridge was closed for nearly 40
OL,15,Fhours in October 2022.
OL,17,FA second man, Morgan Trowland, was
OL,18,Falso jailed for three years for the
OL,19,Fsame offence, after their actions
OL,20,Fmeant more than half a million drivers
OL,21,Ffaced delays and disruption.
