OL,6,FThe pair used ropes and other climbing
OL,7,Fequipment to shuffle up the cables of
OL,8,Fthe bridge, which links the M25 in
OL,9,FEssex and Kent, on October 17.
OL,11,FAt the time of sentencing, Judge Shane
OL,12,FCollery KC said the two caused 'chaos'.
OL,14,FMarcus' partner, Holly Cullen-Davies,
OL,15,Fsays he is now at risk of deportation
OL,16,Fby the British Government due to his
OL,17,Fcitizenship status.
OL,19,FThis, she says, would separate him
OL,20,Ffrom his family and home.
