OL,6,FWriting on change.org, she described
OL,7,Fhim as a wonderful stepfather and
OL,8,Finspiring teacher. She said: "It isn't
OL,9,Feasy for Marcus in prison and it is
OL,10,Fdesperately sad for my family. We miss
OL,11,Fhim every day.
OL,13,F"But as if such a high prison sentence
OL,14,Fwas not bad enough, Marcus, a German
OL,15,Fcitizen, is now being threatened with
OL,16,Fdeportation.
OL,18,F"This double punishment is devastating
OL,19,Ffor us. If deported, he would be
OL,20,Fseparated from us, his family, his
OL,21,Fhome, community and adopted country.
