OL,6,F"Marcus put his own liberty and body
OL,7,Fon the line for those suffering from
OL,8,Fthe climate crisis.
OL,10,F"But he is more than just an activist
OL,11,F- anyone that knows Marcus knows he is
OL,12,Fa gentle, thoughtful and compassionate
OL,13,Fhuman being who would only act
OL,14,Fproportionately to the crisis we all
OL,15,Fface.
OL,17,F"This is the man that I love. A man
OL,18,Fwho sang my children to sleep at
OL,19,Fnight."
