OL,6,FAt the time, the actions of Marcus and
OL,7,FMorgan disrupted over half a million
OL,8,Fmotorists during the 38 hours they
OL,9,Fwere up on the bridge.
OL,11,FEssex Police said those affected by
OL,12,Fthe disruption included a "heavily
OL,13,Fpregnant woman who needed urgent
OL,14,Fmedical help".
OL,16,FAnother person missed the funeral of
OL,17,Ftheir best friend of 35 years, the
OL,18,Fforce said, and a business lost more
OL,19,Fthan #160,000 in earnings.
