OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Louise
OL,7,FMetcalfe, who oversaw the police
OL,8,Finvestigation, said: "Trowland and
OL,9,FDecker's actions were completely
OL,10,Funacceptable. They were dangerous and
OL,11,Fthey were incredibly disruptive.
OL,13,F"We know they saw their actions as
OL,14,Fprotest ` they were not. They caused
OL,15,Fdanger and disruption to many.
OL,17,F"Thankfully, our specially trained
OL,18,Fofficers were able to bring the
OL,19,Fincident to a safe conclusion."
