OL,6,FITV Meridian contacted the Home Office
OL,7,Ffor comment on Marcus Decker's
OL,8,Fsituation and a spokesperson said:
OL,9,F"The right to protest is a fundamental
OL,10,Fpart of our democracy but we must also
OL,11,Fprotect the law-abiding majority's
OL,12,Fright to go about their daily lives.
OL,14,F"Any foreign national who is convicted
OL,15,Fof a crime and given a prison sentence
OL,16,Fis considered for deportation at the
OL,17,Fearliest opportunity."
